WEBVTT

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:30.776
can help health care systems
save more lives.

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:33.016
Their ability to do that is strengthened

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:35.216
when they're enabled
with modern technology.

00:04:35.240 --> 00:04:38.176
Woman: Now, she's saying
that the child has improved

00:04:38.200 --> 00:04:39.856
and went to school today.

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:44.016
